<h2>Accommodation</h2>
<br/>
<p>
Accommodation will be provided to <i>registered</i> participants on a
first-come first-served basis. Please mail your request to
  <a href="mailto:sksisical@gmail.com">sksisical@gmail.com</a>
with a copy to <a href="mailto:clia@isical.ac.in">CLIA</a>.
<b>Please be sure to include your name, affiliation, gender, arrival and
departure times.</b>
</p><br/>
<!-- p>
6 single rooms available in the ISEC hostel, ISI Campus>
</p><br -->
<p>
15 double rooms (twin-sharing basis) are available at the NSSO Guest House,
Mahalanobis Bhawan, 164 G.L.T. Road, Kolkata-700108 (10 minutes walking
distance from the ISI campus).
  <ul>
    <li>Room rent: Rs. 300/- per double room per day</li>
    <li>Check-in / check-out time: 12 noon </li>
    <li>All rooms are equipped with an AC and a geyser.</li>
    <li>Meals are available in the guest house, but may need to be ordered
    in advance.</li>
  </ul>
</p><br/>

